Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:51.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(200,200)}儚き印よ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:54.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(200,200)}砂上に　この地に
